flowRoot.flowPara: 1.Make a drawing inside the circle. It can represent somthing you would like to help someone with, something you would like help with, or simply something you really like.
2.Find a friend that can design the other side of the coin on another piece of paper.
3.Scan the drawings with our collaborative currency scanner at bitraf.
4.Digitally fabricate your coin and use it for something meaningful, or go buy a beer with it in our collaborative BeeBar at Kulturhuset (17:00 - 19:00)
